Actions.Text: REFERRED TO HOUSING, CONSTRUCTION AND COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT

Title: Authorizes the state of New York to enter into the interstate compact on industrialized/modular buildings
Summary: Authorizes the state of New York to enter into the interstate compact on industrialized/modular buildings which provides for uniform regulations on industrialized/modular homes.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the executive law, in relation to adopting the interstate compact on industrialized/modular buildings
